{
  "texts": [
    "We also test a range of other models.",
    "Fifth and last, we will discuss how we construct our policy-linkage indices from our textual corpus.",
    "The purpose of this paper is to develop indices which identify policy linkages in central bank communication.",
    "These indices not only identify policy linkages but also determine their nature (policy coordination or dominance) over time and across central banks.",
    "Identifying these patterns from text is a complex reasoning task that requires substantial domain knowledge."
  ]
}